        "description": "This data has 15 minute interval simulated thermal power-station generated electricity load data for a particular grid from Indian Power Generation Company. This data mainly serves for forecasting playground to achieve greater ac-curacies (+-5%).\n1) Day_Interval - \"%d-%b-%Y %H:%M\" format for every 15 Minute Interval.\n2) Frequency_in_Hz - Electricity generated measured in Hz frequency.\n3) Penalty for under generation in Indian Rupees.\n\nOther Datasets by Author:\nDaily Store Sales and Revenue of 600 plus SKUs - [Link](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/pradeep13/daily-store-sales-and-revenue-of-600-plus-skus)\n\n=== About this file ===\n\nAbout this file\nIt has three columns:\n1) Day_Interval - \"%d-%b-%Y %H:%M\" format for every 15 Minute Interval.\n2) Frequency_in_Hz - Electricity generated measured in Hz frequency.\n3) Penalty for under generation in Indian Rupees.\nPS: Sort Day_Interval after converting to appropriate Date-Time format.\n\n\n=== Columns & descriptions ===\n\nDay_Interval: 03-Mar-2018 00:15\nFrequency_in_Hz: 49.9\nUI_Penalty_INR_per_kwh: 3006.5\n",
